wobani.resources.splines

Class SplinePoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • wobani.resources.splines.SplinePoint

  • public class SplinePoint
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a left and a right helper point to a control point. It could be helpful for example for Bezier curves.
